00:01:46.520 --> 00:01:46.920
Prin-

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:47.580
Principal.

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:49.240
I just...

00:01:52.320 --> 00:01:53.479
Manman.

00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:55.720
You've learned to lie.

00:01:57.200 --> 00:01:58.130
Do you know that?

00:01:59.320 --> 00:02:01.680
I hate it most when others deceive me

00:02:01.800 --> 00:02:02.880
and betray me.

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:08.000
Take her away.

00:02:32.960 --> 00:02:33.620
Principal,

00:02:33.880 --> 00:02:34.520
I was wrong.

00:02:34.520 --> 00:02:35.520
I won't dare to do it again.

00:02:35.520 --> 00:02:36.800
Please forgive me.

00:02:37.440 --> 00:02:39.770
It's good that you know you made a mistake.

00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:42.200
I treat you so well.

00:02:43.079 --> 00:02:45.210
I bought you so many clothes and gifts.

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:48.560
I gave you everything you have today.

00:02:48.640 --> 00:02:49.720
I know.

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:51.400
So everything you have belongs to me.

00:02:51.400 --> 00:02:52.120
Do you understand?

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:53.240
I know I was wrong.

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:54.300
I won't do it again.

00:02:54.480 --> 00:02:55.720
I won't do it again.

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:56.240
Good.

00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:57.800
Just be obedient.

00:02:59.400 --> 00:03:00.600
If there are rewards,

00:03:00.640 --> 00:03:01.920
