00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:03.360
Students who make mistakes

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:04.800
must go to the dark room.

00:03:05.280 --> 00:03:06.010
Do you agree?

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:09.600
Get up.

00:03:17.079 --> 00:03:17.810
Does it hurt?

00:03:18.320 --> 00:03:18.960
No.

00:03:22.480 --> 00:03:23.880
When I come back tonight,

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:26.500
I'll help you apply the medicine.

00:03:33.320 --> 00:03:33.960
Go inside.

00:03:55.720 --> 00:03:56.840
Reflect on

00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:58.460
what you did wrong.

00:03:59.360 --> 00:04:00.760
I'll pick you up tonight.

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:34.240
Manman.

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:37.730
Qian Manman.

00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:41.290
Qian Manman.

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:42.260
Who are you?

00:04:42.400 --> 00:04:43.400
How did you get in?

00:04:43.560 --> 00:04:44.620
What are you doing?

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:54.240
Manman.

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:03.720
You... you...

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:04.680
Who are you?

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:38.880
An uncle gave this to me.

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:40.680
He said he's your good friend.

00:05:41.320 --> 00:05:44.720
Anjia Neighborhood, Building 4, Unit 4, Apartment 404.

00:05:45.240 --> 00:05:47.170
Yinghuochong After-School Care.

00:05:47.760 --> 00:05:49.090
If you don't want to die,

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:51.040
someone else will.

00:05:51.400 --> 00:05:53.130
It might just be your daughter.

00:05:53.200 --> 00:05:55.159
She's alone far too often.

00:05:58.800 --> 00:06:00.060
I don't dare to go home.

00:06:00.920 --> 00:06:02.560
