00:06:03.880 --> 00:06:04.480
Manman.

00:06:05.040 --> 00:06:06.440
Don't be afraid.

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:08.240
The person who saved us said

00:06:08.240 --> 00:06:09.480
if we hide for a few days,

00:06:09.480 --> 00:06:10.880
it will all pass.

00:06:11.200 --> 00:06:11.760
Can we

00:06:11.760 --> 00:06:13.200
trust him?

00:06:20.640 --> 00:06:21.700
What else can we do?

00:06:22.600 --> 00:06:24.040
We have no other choice.

00:06:25.240 --> 00:06:26.840
Even if we went to the police,

00:06:27.040 --> 00:06:28.600
the few photos we have

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:31.960
can't prove we were not willing.

00:06:33.880 --> 00:06:35.940
We still can't arrest Zhang Wendong.

00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:42.580
Does underwear

00:06:42.920 --> 00:06:43.980
count as evidence?

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:45.120
What underwear?

00:06:45.159 --> 00:06:45.840
Last time

00:06:45.880 --> 00:06:47.140
he took me to his place.

00:06:47.240 --> 00:06:49.040
I was so panicked when I got back.

00:06:49.400 --> 00:06:49.840
The clothes

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:50.560
were just

00:06:50.760 --> 00:06:53.090
thrown there and haven't been washed yet.

00:06:53.440 --> 00:06:55.300
There seems to be something on it.

00:06:58.720 --> 00:07:01.120
This is the person looking for Captain Sun.

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:04.240
Hello.

00:07:05.440 --> 00:07:06.570
What can I do for you?

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:20.560
Liu Jiang!

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:22.090
Put the bag down.

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:24.740
Hands on your head.

00:07:24.880 --> 00:07:25.540
Squat down.

00:07:39.480 --> 00:07:40.210
Captain Sun.

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:40.970
Captain Sun.

00:07:41.560 --> 00:07:42.290
Captain Sun.

00:07:42.400 --> 00:07:43.000
Yan,

00:07:43.320 --> 00:07:45.120
Liu Jiang has turned himself in.

00:07:49.440 --> 00:07:50.000
Got it.

00:07:50.680 --> 00:07:52.440
Take him to the interrogation room.

00:07:52.440 --> 00:07:53.500
What's the matter?

00:07:56.240 --> 00:07:57.040
Calm down.

00:07:57.560 --> 00:07:58.720
I am very calm right now.

00:07:58.720 --> 00:08:00.360
Jia Peng died because of Liu Jiang.

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:01.680
So I must interrogate him myself.

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:02.760
How will you interrogate him?

00:08:02.760 --> 00:08:04.320
Liu Jiang dug up the grave and burned the corpse.

00:08:04.320 --> 00:08:05.520
He hid out there for so long,

00:08:05.520 --> 00:08:06.800
and now suddenly comes back to turn himself in.

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:08.200
Have you thought about his motive?

00:08:08.200 --> 00:08:09.960
Do you have calm thinking and judgment right now?

00:08:09.960 --> 00:08:11.080
That's because he was outside.

00:08:11.080 --> 00:08:12.240
He could die at any time.

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:13.680
Only the police will protect him.

00:08:13.680 --> 00:08:14.760
If he only wanted to live,

00:08:14.760 --> 00:08:15.960
why did he fake his death?

00:08:15.960 --> 00:08:18.490
Wouldn't it be better to just turn himself in?

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:23.160
Think carefully.

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:24.840
What else

00:08:25.920 --> 00:08:27.040
don't we know?

00:08:31.760 --> 00:08:32.440
Photos.

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:34.440
Guan Jing's death

00:08:34.919 --> 00:08:36.850
must have something to do with him.

00:08:43.360 --> 00:08:43.960
Let's go.

00:08:54.920 --> 00:08:56.520
Why did you turn yourself in?

00:08:57.080 --> 00:08:57.760
I want

00:08:59.280 --> 00:08:59.840
to live.

00:09:01.280 --> 00:09:01.940
And also...

00:09:02.920 --> 00:09:04.780
