00:09:14.320 --> 00:09:14.880
He...

00:09:15.880 --> 00:09:17.680
In order to save you at that time,

00:09:17.720 --> 00:09:19.050
he didn't even hesitate

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:20.730
and pushed you away.

00:09:21.920 --> 00:09:23.360
To protect the innocent,

00:09:25.360 --> 00:09:27.420
he covered the bomb with his own body.

00:09:28.640 --> 00:09:30.500
Are you worthy of a life like that?

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:35.040
He...

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:35.880
died?

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:37.360
He just graduated.

00:09:43.040 --> 00:09:43.720
I'm sorry.

00:09:45.040 --> 00:09:46.770
I don't know who threw the bomb.

00:09:47.640 --> 00:09:48.770
I just remember him,

00:09:48.840 --> 00:09:49.560
this police officer,

00:09:49.560 --> 00:09:50.560
in order to save me,

00:09:50.560 --> 00:09:52.220
he threw himself at that bomb.

00:09:55.200 --> 00:09:56.660
It was a misunderstanding

00:09:57.560 --> 00:09:58.960
about the police officer.

00:09:58.960 --> 00:10:00.760
Your daughter's life is a life,

00:10:01.240 --> 00:10:03.440
but are our police officers' lives not?

00:10:04.520 --> 00:10:05.200
I'm sorry.

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:07.540
It's a misunderstanding.

00:10:09.200 --> 00:10:10.280
A misunderstanding.

00:10:10.280 --> 00:10:11.440
Then explain it clearly from the beginning.

00:10:11.440 --> 00:10:12.560
How many secrets are hidden

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:14.090
in your misunderstanding?

00:10:14.440 --> 00:10:15.240
I'll confess.

00:10:15.520 --> 00:10:16.980
I'll confess everything.

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:19.720
Can I ask you

00:10:19.720 --> 00:10:20.760
