00:10:21.440 --> 00:10:22.480
Before I confess,

00:10:22.480 --> 00:10:23.760
can you send someone to protect

00:10:23.760 --> 00:10:24.960
my wife and daughter?

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:27.180
I think they are in danger at any time.

00:10:27.760 --> 00:10:28.520
Right now,

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:29.480
send someone to protect them.

00:10:29.480 --> 00:10:30.400
We have already arranged it.

00:10:30.400 --> 00:10:31.040
You can rest assured.

00:10:31.040 --> 00:10:32.800
Thank you.

00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:42.020
I've never killed anyone.

00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:43.520
Never.

00:10:44.400 --> 00:10:45.640
I was just so scared.

00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:48.420
Because Zhang Biao was murdered.

00:10:48.840 --> 00:10:49.400
And...

00:10:49.640 --> 00:10:52.240
They threatened me with my daughter every day.

00:10:52.640 --> 00:10:54.170
I wondered what I should do.

00:10:54.280 --> 00:10:55.280
Nobody helped me.

00:10:56.160 --> 00:10:57.690
I thought I'd just dig a hole

00:10:57.920 --> 00:10:59.080
and dig up a dead body,

00:10:59.080 --> 00:11:00.040
