00:11:02.800 --> 00:11:03.520
Then wouldn't this matter

00:11:03.520 --> 00:11:04.920
be settled once and for all?

00:11:04.920 --> 00:11:06.050
Wouldn't it be over?

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:09.530
What exactly happened in that secret room back then?

00:11:12.320 --> 00:11:12.920
Come here.

00:11:12.960 --> 00:11:14.360
Look at this photo again.

00:11:15.240 --> 00:11:17.000
How did Guan Jing in this photo

00:11:17.840 --> 00:11:18.800
