00:11:22.360 --> 00:11:23.420
It was an accident.

00:11:24.920 --> 00:11:25.840
An accident.

00:11:26.960 --> 00:11:28.080
At that time,

00:11:28.440 --> 00:11:29.920
they took those little girls

00:11:29.920 --> 00:11:30.980
and brought them to

00:11:31.400 --> 00:11:31.920
A Biao's

