His name is Zhang Wendong.

00:12:06.920 --> 00:12:08.650
Zhang Wendong took the photos.

00:12:08.840 --> 00:12:11.170
Zhang Wendong organized the whole thing.

00:12:11.320 --> 00:12:11.880
And...

00:12:12.520 --> 00:12:14.120
