00:12:15.480 --> 00:12:16.480
Principal Zhang.

00:12:16.600 --> 00:12:17.640
There's a slogan,

00:12:17.800 --> 00:12:19.280
"The sun rises red in the east,

00:12:19.280 --> 00:12:21.120
