00:14:38.840 --> 00:14:39.570
Captain Sun.

00:14:40.840 --> 00:14:43.370
I've pulled up Zhang Wendong's information.

00:14:44.360 --> 00:14:44.880
Zhang Wendong,

00:14:44.880 --> 00:14:45.840
45 years old.

