This school

00:14:52.600 --> 00:14:53.600
offers a wide range of services.

00:14:53.600 --> 00:14:54.600
From art exam training

00:14:54.600 --> 00:14:55.440
to signing actors.

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:56.240
