Zhang Wendong himself

00:15:01.120 --> 00:15:01.920
has always claimed to be

00:15:01.920 --> 00:15:03.160
a performing artist.

00:15:03.760 --> 00:15:05.000
He divorced five years ago.

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:07.120
His ex-wife took their daughter to live abroad.

00:15:07.120 --> 00:15:07.880
Rumor has it

00:15:07.880 --> 00:15:08.480
