Zhang Wendong wants to climb the social ladder,

00:15:14.360 --> 00:15:14.840
so

00:15:14.840 --> 00:15:16.360
he needs to erase all his blemishes.

00:15:16.360 --> 00:15:17.520
We also found out that

00:15:17.520 --> 00:15:18.680
Guan Jing and Li Ting,

00:15:18.680 --> 00:15:20.400
before entering the KTV in 2004,

00:15:20.400 --> 00:15:21.600
both briefly stayed

00:15:21.640 --> 00:15:22.440
at Richu Dongfang.

00:15:22.440 --> 00:15:22.840
Right.

00:15:22.960 --> 00:15:24.520
These are all common tricks

00:15:24.520 --> 00:15:25.400
of Richu Dongfang.

