telling them

00:15:28.920 --> 00:15:30.120
they could participate for free

00:15:30.120 --> 00:15:30.600
in acting

00:15:30.600 --> 00:15:31.860
or modeling training.

00:15:31.880 --> 00:15:33.160
But very few of them actually

00:15:33.160 --> 00:15:34.560
became actors or models.

00:15:34.600 --> 00:15:36.200
We interviewed a few of them.

00:15:36.400 --> 00:15:37.120
But

00:15:37.240 --> 00:15:38.770
they seemed very reluctant

00:15:38.800 --> 00:15:40.720
to talk about their experiences at the art school.

00:15:40.720 --> 00:15:42.440
Zhang Wendong is deeply

00:15:42.800 --> 00:15:43.880
involved in this incident.

00:15:43.880 --> 00:15:45.560
He definitely knows something.

00:15:45.560 --> 00:15:46.420
Bring him back.

00:15:46.880 --> 00:15:47.880
I want to see

00:15:48.240 --> 00:15:49.320
how good this performing artist's

00:15:49.320 --> 00:15:50.320
acting really is.

00:15:54.440 --> 00:15:55.040
Qiao Sisi.

00:15:56.520 --> 00:15:57.250
Captain Sun.

00:15:59.000 --> 00:16:00.520
I went to get Zhang Wendong's files.

00:16:00.520 --> 00:16:01.120
Coincidentally,

00:16:01.120 --> 00:16:02.360
Nanqiao Police Station received

